trans-unit.source: You can use the <ui>Convert to TSV</ui> module to convert any dataset from the internal format that is used by all Azure Machine Learning Studio modules, to a flat file in tab-separated format.

trans-unit.source: The <externalLink><linkText>Cross Validation for Binary Classification sample</linkText><linkUri>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=525734</linkUri></externalLink> exports the results of cross validation to the comma-separated value (CSV) format so that results for multiple models can be compared by using a tool such as Excel.

trans-unit.source: The <externalLink><linkText>Color-Based Image Compression Quantization</linkText><linkUri>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=525272</linkUri></externalLink> sample exports the datasets that are used for each portion of the analysis to CSV files, so that you can easily run a similar model in any tool that supports the CSV format.

trans-unit.source: Tab-separated values (TSV) is a text format that is used to store data in a tabular structure.
trans-unit.target: Tab-separated values (TSV) is a text format that is used to store data in a tabular structure.

trans-unit.source: It is very similar to the CSV format, but the delimiter is a tab rather than a comma.
trans-unit.target: It is very similar to the CSV format, but the delimiter is a tab rather than a comma.

trans-unit.source: The TSV format is a useful alternative to the CSV format if your data contains commas.
trans-unit.target: The TSV format is a useful alternative to the CSV format if your data contains commas.

trans-unit.source: Commas are very common in text data and they are used in European number formats.
trans-unit.target: Commas are very common in text data and they are used in European number formats.

trans-unit.source: One problem with the tab-delimited format is that tab stops are frequently considered as white space in unstructured text.
trans-unit.target: One problem with the tab-delimited format is that tab stops are frequently considered as white space in unstructured text.

trans-unit.source: However, the IANA standard for TSV fosters clean and accurate parsing of TSV files by disallowing tabs within fields.
trans-unit.target: However, the IANA standard for TSV fosters clean and accurate parsing of TSV files by disallowing tabs within fields.

trans-unit.source: The <ui>Convert to TSV</ui> module supports the output of a single heading row, if the dataset contains column names.
trans-unit.target: The <ui>Convert to TSV</ui> module supports the output of a single heading row, if the dataset contains column names.

trans-unit.source: The TSV provider supports UTF-8 character encoding only.
trans-unit.target: The TSV provider supports UTF-8 character encoding only.

trans-unit.source: When reading from or writing to TSV files, performance can be slower than with other formats (such as CSV).
trans-unit.target: When reading from or writing to TSV files, performance can be slower than with other formats (such as CSV).
